data.description: If you are looking to downsize with little to no maintenance or if you are looking for a great rental property...then you need to view this condo! The location can't be beat! This charming condo sits just off Ocoee Street, in the heart of the city and is close to Lee University. Complete with 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, attic storage AND a 2-car garage!  The primary bedroom is on the main floor and has a private bath, walk-in closet, and access to a private courtyard with a covered trellis.  Just upstairs you will find 2 additional bedrooms, 1 and a half baths AND attic storage. The home has a new HVAC, new hot water heater, new garage door opener, new outside lights and with the parking in the driveway and the garage this unit has a total of 6 parking spaces. There is also a large community common grounds lot right beside the unit, so you have a big yard with no maintenance!  Schedule your private showing today!
